b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk?\n#LouisVuitton\xe2\x80\x99s trunk-making heritage can be found throughout the Maison\xe2\x80\x99s diverse creations. With the launch of #LVParfums, travel cases protect the growing collection of fragrances.'

b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk?\nOver 160 years ago, #LouisVuitton began designing trunks specifically around the objects they would contain. Today, the Maison continues to use time-honed skills and specialized techniques to craft cases for a range of objects, such as a complete Chinese tea ceremony set.'

b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk? #LouisVuitton\xe2\x80\x99s training as a box maker and packer inspired him to later imagine innovative hard-sided cases for both everyday and imaginative creations. Swipe to discover the intricately detailed Malle Maison Vivienne.'

b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk?\n#LouisVuitton constantly searches for new ways to pack and protect precious belongings and thoughtful gifts. One particular trunk has everything needed for a birthday celebration with an insulated case for cake as well as candles and silverware.'

b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk?\nThroughout the years, #LouisVuitton\xe2\x80\x99s hard-sided creations have taken on many forms and sizes. A mini format opens to reveal a poetic music box featuring a twirling Vivienne figurine.'

b'What\xe2\x80\x99s in the trunk?\n#LouisVuitton founded his namesake Maison in 1854 as an expert and innovative trunk maker. Swipe to see how that legacy of exceptional savoir-faire lives on today in a selection of modern creations. In the 1910s, Gaston-Louis Vuitton would give his most loyal clients a specially-outfitted trunk filled with fresh flowers, a tradition that inspired the modern Malle Fleurs.'

b"LV Cine Club with #ChloeGraceMoretz
#LouisVuitton's ambassadors are sharing a current selection of movies and series to watch while at home.

Chloe\xcc\x88\xe2\x80\x99s picks:

Narcos, Carlo Bernard, Chris Brancato & Doug Miro
\xc2\xab The acting is impeccable and it\xe2\x80\x99s a great one to binge because there are so many incredible seasons and then you can go straight into Narcos Mexico after you finish the original narcos series.\xc2\xa0\xc2\xbb

Killing Eve, Phoebe Waller-Bridge
\xc2\xab Phoebe Waller-Bridge creating anything seems to be perfect!! This show ticks all the boxes for me from character driven drama to wild action fight sequences. And phenomenal acting to boot!\xc2\xa0\xc2\xbb

Westworld, Jonathan Nolan
\xc2\xab\xc2\xa0Such a decadent world to be able to jump into, each episode really feels like a stand alone movie in of itself.  And the twists and turns no matter how many times I watch it over still get me!\xc2\xa0\xc2\xbb

Godfather I & II, Francis Ford Coppola
\xc2\xab 6 hours in total, truly exceptional film making and acting, it is  so worth it. Order some Italian food, pour a glass of red wine and soak it in!  You\xe2\x80\x99ll be feeling like you\xe2\x80\x99re apart of this world by the end of them both! .\xc2\xa0\xc2\xbb

Rick and Morty, Justin Roitland & Dan Harmson
\xc2\xab When you need a break from the serious stuff Rick and Morty I always find comes through and makes me laugh about how intricate and brilliant the writing is on this show.\xc2\xa0\xc2\xbb"

b"LV Cine Club with #SophieTurner. 
#LouisVuitton's ambassadors are sharing a current selection of movies and series to watch while at home.

Sophie\xe2\x80\x99s picks:

The Lord of the Rings (I,II & III), Peter Jackson
\xc2\xab It\xe2\x80\x99s an epic fantasy series of movies with a whole lot of escapism which is what people need right now, and a long run time. \xc2\xbb

Goodfellas , Martin Scorcese
\xc2\xab I love a gangster movie and it\xe2\x80\x99s absolutely one of my favorite movies with some iconic performances from Robert De Niro, Ray Liotta and Joe Pesci. \xc2\xbb

One Flew Over the Cuckoos Nest, Milos Forman
\xc2\xab This is another one of my favorite movies. It\xe2\x80\x99s prime 70s Jack Nicholson with an incredible cast supporting him and some unbelievable performances while commenting on the mental health care system of the 70s. It won all five major academy awards. \xc2\xbb

Onward\xe2\x80\x8b, Dan Scanlon
\xc2\xab On the lighter side, I loved Onward. It\xe2\x80\x99s a great Disney Pixar movie with, as per usual, wonderful animation and a really heartwarming story. \xc2\xbb

This Country, Tom George
\xc2\xab This is another lighter watch. It\xe2\x80\x99s a brilliantly side-splittingly funny mockumentary about two young people living in the rural English countryside. \xc2\xbb"

b'At Louis Vuitton, we have always believed in the inspiration that comes from traveling the world.

Given the current challenge that every community on our shared planet is facing, we know that the road ahead can seem uncertain and such optimistic journeys far from the mind.

Right now, the most important thing is each other.
We want to take this opportunity to wish you health, safety, and hope to get through this time together.

We believe in the journey, even the ones that for now take flight in our dream.

Sincerely,
the family at #LouisVuitton'
